text: Stanisław Karczewski (born 14 November 1955) is a Polish politician and surgeon. He has been a senator since 2005, as Deputy Marshal of the Senate between 2011 and 2015 and since 2019, and between 2015 and 2019 as Marshal of the Senate of the Republic of Poland. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Marshals of the Senate of the Republic of Poland
title: Stanisław Karczewski
